# 📊 Economic Trends Dashboard

An interactive Power BI/Excel dashboard that visualizes long-term trends in key economic indicators like GDP growth, inflation, and unemployment across countries.

---

## 📁 Files
- `economic_trends.pbix` – Main Power BI file
- `dataset.xlsx` – Cleaned economic data
- `sample_dashboard.png` – Preview of the dashboard

---

## 📈 Dashboard Highlights
- 20-year trend analysis of GDP, inflation, and unemployment
- Country-wise comparison and global averages
- KPI cards for latest available values
- Slicers for region and indicator type

---

## 📊 Data Source
- [World Bank Open Data](https://data.worldbank.org/)


## 🛠 Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel

